Package: mediationr2
Type: Package
Title: R2-Based Effect Sizes and Power Analysis for Mediation Models
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Heqiao", "Ruan", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "you@example.com")
  )
Description: Utilities for simulating mediation-model data and conducting bootstrap-based
    power analysis using R2-type effect sizes for linear models and deviance-based pseudo-R2
    measures for generalized linear models.
